Title: Yang-Baxter Equation on Two-Dimensional Lattice and Some Infinite

Dimensional AlgebrasAuthors: M. Daoud, J. Douari and Y. Hassouni

Comments: 14 pages

Journal-ref: acta physica slovaca, vol.49 No.6, 945 (1999)

We show that the Yang-Baxter equation is equivalent to the associativity ofthe algebra generated by non-commuting link operators. Starting from these linkoperators we build out the (FFZ) algebras, the $s\ell_q (2)$ is derived byconsidering a special combination of the generators of (FFZ) algebra.